PrecisOrder fixing WEDNESDAY, NOVEMBER 1, 1995, as the day upon which the Government Organization Act (Federal Agencies) shall COME INTO FORCE, except for sections 4 and 5 (Canadian Broadcasting Corporation) which shall come into force on January 1, 1996, and sections 23 and 32 (Emergency Preparedness Canada) which shall come into force on April 1, 1996.

precis:
Order fixing WEDNESDAY, NOVEMBER 1, 1995, as the day upon which the
Government Organization Act (Federal Agencies) shall COME INTO FORCE,
except for sections 4 and 5 (Canadian Broadcasting Corporation) which shall
come into force on January 1, 1996, and sections 23 and 32 (Emergency
Preparedness Canada) which shall come into force on April 1, 1996.
